<inglise> 3.2.1. </inglise>
<eesti> 3.2.1. </eesti>
<inglise> General comments </inglise>
<eesti> &Uuml;ldised m&auml;rkused </eesti>
<inglise> The manufacturer must have or have available the installations, equipment and personnel which enable him to carry out the necessary verifications and tests. </inglise>
<eesti> Tootjal peavad olema etten&auml;htud vastavuse t&otilde;endamiseks ja katseteks vajalikud seadmed, vahendid ja t&ouml;&ouml;tajad v&otilde;i tal peab olema v&otilde;imalus neid kasutada. </eesti>
<inglise> He may, as may his agent, meet this requirement by concluding a sub-contracting agreement with one or more organisations or persons having the necessary skills and equipment. </inglise>
<eesti> Tootja v&otilde;i tema esindaja v&otilde;ib selle n&otilde;ude t&auml;itmiseks s&otilde;lmida ka allt&ouml;&ouml;v&otilde;tulepingu &uuml;he v&otilde;i mitme asutuse v&otilde;i isikuga, kellel on vajalikud oskused ja seadmed. </eesti>
<inglise> The manufacturer must calibrate or verify and maintain the control, measuring or test equipment in good operating condition, whether or not it belongs to him, with a view to demonstrating conformity of the product with its technical specification. </inglise>
<eesti> Et t&otilde;endada toote vastavust tehnilisele kirjeldusele, peab tootja kalibreerima kontrolli-, m&otilde;&otilde;te- ja katseseadmed v&otilde;i t&otilde;endama nende n&otilde;uetele vastavust ning hoidma need heas t&ouml;&ouml;korras olenemata sellest, kas ta on nende omanik v&otilde;i mitte. </eesti>
<inglise> The equipment must be used in conformity with the specification or the test reference system to which the specification refers. </inglise>
